《传送门》的流行使維爾福通过在线[[Steam|Steam]]商店售卖《传送门》风格的实体商品，例如广受欢迎的同伴方块毛绒玩具和{{link-en|模糊骰子|fuzzy dice}}。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.steampowered.com/Steam/Marketing/message/1301/ | title = Steam Updates: Friday, November 9, 2007 | date = 2007-11-09 | accessdate = 2007-11-09 | publisher = Valve | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071111201436/http://www.steampowered.com/Steam/Marketing/message/1301/ | archive-date = 2007-11-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>当他们第一次开卖时，不到24小时就销售一空。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/gaming/sold-out/official-plush-weighted-companion-cube-sells-out-334413.php | title = Official Plush Weighted Companion Cube Sells Out | date = 2007-12-15 | accessdate = 2008-02-21 | publisher = Kotaku | first = Flynn | last = De Marco | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080304073947/http://kotaku.com/gaming/sold-out/official-plush-weighted-companion-cube-sells-out-334413.php | archive-date = 2008-03-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>其他产品例如T恤衫、咖啡杯、贴纸也可从維爾福商店购买。其中“the cake is a lie”成为了[[網路爆紅|网络迷因]]，不过编剧艾瑞克·沃保对此感到意外，因为他们原本希望玩家能够关注游戏结束时在屏幕上跳动的那个铁圈，还特地取名“Hoopy”，结果玩家却把铁圈忽略了。<ref name="gi portal hl" />

== 發行 ==

=== 演示版 ===
2008年1月，維爾福发布了名为“'''Portal: The First Slice'''”的演示版本，其中包括了实验室0到实验室10，玩家可免费下载试玩。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://store.steampowered.com/news/1570/ | title = Everyday Shooter Makes PC Debut on Steam Today | date = 2008-05-08 | accessdate = 2008-05-15 | publisher = Valve | quote = In other Steam news, Portal: First Slice – the official demo for the title named Game of the Year by over 30 publications – is now available for free to all gamers via Steam. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080921191927/http://store.steampowered.com/news/1570/ | archive-date = 2008-09-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>作为与[[Nvidia|Nvidia]]公司的合作计划，使用[[Nvidia|Nvidia]]显卡的[[Steam|Steam]]玩家可以免费下载包括《Portal: The First Slice》、《[[戰慄時空2：死鬥模式|戰慄時空2：死鬥模式]]》、《[[戰慄時空2：消失的海岸線|戰慄時空2：消失的海岸線]]》和《[[Peggle_Extreme|Peggle Extreme]]》在内的游戏。<ref name="Steam News 1398">{{cite web | url = http://store.steampowered.com/news/1398/ | title = Valve and NVIDIA Offer Portal: First Slice Free to GeForce Users | accessdate = 2010-08-11 | date = 2008-01-09 | work = [[Steam|Steam]] | publisher = [[Valve|Valve]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100716095417/http://store.steampowered.com/news/1398 | archive-date = 2010-07-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.g-cores.com/articles/19703|title=真没想到当年《传送门》的测试版是这样的|publisher=|access-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306035827/http://www.g-cores.com/articles/19703|archive-date=2017-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 传送门 ===
《传送门》最初作为[[橙盒|橙盒]]的一部分于2007年10月9日发行，包括[[Windows|Windows]]系统和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台，<ref name="pcrelease" /><ref name="360release" />2007年12月11日发布[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]平台版本。<ref name="ps3release" />Windows版也可以通过[[Steam|Steam]]购买和下载，<ref name="Steam App 400">{{cite web | url = http://store.steampowered.com/app/400/ | title = Portal | accessdate = 2010-08-11 | work = [[Steam_(software)|Steam]] | publisher = [[Valve_Corporation|Valve Corporation]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100810224001/http://store.steampowered.com/app/400 | archive-date = 2010-08-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>于2008年4月9日发布[[零售|零售]]版本。<ref name="joystiq orange split" />零售版在北美由[[美商藝電|EA]]發行，在[[台灣|台灣]]則由[[松崗科技|松崗科技]]代理發行，橘盒命名為重裝旗艦包。

对于維爾福而言，将《传送门》与《[[半条命2：第二章|半条命2：第二章]]》、《[[军团要塞2|军团要塞2]]》捆绑销售是一次营销上的试验。他们并不知道《传送门》能否成功，所以这样做会“保险”一些。而且游戏的定价也不太高以免因玩家不满而失败。<ref name="gi p2 reveal">{{cite news | title = Portal 2 | first = Meagan | last= VanBurkleo | date = April 2010 | pages = 50–62 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]}}</ref>后来才发布零售版本。

2010年5月12日，在Steam发布Mac版客户端时，《传送门》是在維爾福开发的游戏中第一批支持[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]系统的游戏。，<ref name="Hollister" />并支持Steam Play，也就是说，只要玩家购买了游戏，不管是[[苹果电脑|苹果电脑]]还是普通电脑，都可以直接下载。作为促销手段，两周之内，只要使用Mac版Steam，就可以免费玩到《传送门》。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/28529/Steam_Launched_For_Mac_Portal_Offered_For_Free.php | title = Steam Launched For Mac, Portal Offered For Free | first = Eric | last = Caolli | date = 2010-05-12 | accessdate = 2010-05-13 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100513031836/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/28529/Steam_Launched_For_Mac_Portal_Offered_For_Free.php | archive-date = 2010-05-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>促销的第一周，《传送门》在Steam上就被下载了150万次。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/28626/Portal_Racks_Up_15M_Free_Downloads_On_PC_Mac.php | title = Portal Racks Up 1.5M Free Downloads On PC, Mac | first = Chris | last = Remo | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2010-05-19 | accessdate = 2010-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100521034012/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/28626/Portal_Racks_Up_15M_Free_Downloads_On_PC_Mac.php | archive-date = 2010-05-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2011年9月，接近学校开学的时候，維爾福又做了一次类似的促销，鼓励玩家将游戏用作学习科学和数学的教学工具。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-09-16-portal-free-on-steam-until-20th-sept | title = Portal free on Steam until 20th Sept | first = Robert | last = Purchase | date = 2011-09-16 | accessdate = 2011-09-16 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110923160004/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-09-16-portal-free-on-steam-until-20th-sept | archive-date = 2011-09-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.learningwithportals.com | title=Learn With Portals | work=learningwithportals.com | publisher=Valve Corporation | date=2011-09-15 | accessdate=2014-04-27 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006153050/http://learningwithportals.com/ | archivedate=2011-10-06 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>維爾福评论道《传送门》“使物理学、数学、逻辑学、空间推理、概率和解题变得生动有趣”。这些知识和能力是一个儿童所必需的。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2011/09/portal-is-used-to-teach-science-as-valve-gives-game-away-for-limited-time.ars | title = Portal is used to teach science as Valve gives game away for limited time | first = Ben | last = Kuchera | date = 2011-09-16 | accessdate = 2011-09-16 | publisher = Ars Technica | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120126224405/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2011/09/portal-is-used-to-teach-science-as-valve-gives-game-away-for-limited-time.ars | archive-date = 2012-01-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>美国教育部提倡开发用于教育领域的电子工具，維爾福即响应了这个倡议。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/09/valve-teams-with-white-house-in-digital-learning-program/1 | title = Valve teams with White House in digital learning program | first = Greg | last = Toppo | date = 2011-09-19 | accessdate = 2011-09-20 | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110921155713/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/09/valve-teams-with-white-house-in-digital-learning-program/1 | archive-date = 2011-09-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2014年3月25日举办的[[GPU技术大会|GPU技术大会]]上，[[Nvidia|Nvidia]]宣布他们将通过[[Nvidia_Shield|Nvidia Shield]]方案把《传送门》移植到[[Android|Android]]系统中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/2014/03/25/portal-shield/|title=What’s in the Box? Portal – Valve’s Popular PC Title – Coming to SHIELD|last=Paul|first=Jason|date=2014-03-25|publisher=[[英伟达|Nvidia]]|accessdate=2014-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605013705/http://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/2014/03/25/portal-shield/|archive-date=2014-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>移植版于2014年5月12日发布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/5/26/5745304/why-nvidia-is-developing-games-and-creating-its-own-hardware-platform|title=Why Nvidia created its own hardware platform and started developing games|last=Tach|first=Dave|date=2014-05-26|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2014-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527214519/http://www.polygon.com/2014/5/26/5745304/why-nvidia-is-developing-games-and-creating-its-own-hardware-platform|archive-date=2014-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 传送门：仍然活着 ===
2008年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]大会上，維爾福宣布《传送门：仍然活着》将作为[[Xbox_Live_Arcade|Xbox Live Arcade]]游戏发布。10月22日游戏正式发布，<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/55376 | title = Portal: Still Alive Hits Xbox Live Arcade Next Wed; Promises Cake and Companionship | publisher = Shacknews | date = 2008-10-16 | accessdate = 2008-10-16 | first = Chris | last = Faylor | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081017221912/http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/55376 | archive-date = 2008-10-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>包括原作和14个新关卡，还有新的成就。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/53605 | title = Portal: Still Alive Coming Exclusively to Xbox 360 | first = Chris | last = Faylor | date = 2008-07-14 | accessdate = 2008-07-14 | publisher = Shacknews | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080715152957/http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/53605 | archive-date = 2008-07-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>额外关卡以团队“We Create Stuff”制作的地图包《Portal: The Flash Version》为基础，还有一些關卡与剧情无关。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2008/07/portal_still_alive_explained_1.php | title = Portal: Still Alive Explained | first = Chris | last = Remo | date = 2008-07-20 | accessdate = 2008-07-21 | publisher = GameSetWatch | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080729000856/http://www.gamesetwatch.com/2008/07/portal_still_alive_explained_1.php | archive-date = 2008-07-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>发言人Doug Lombardi表示，[[微软|微软]]起初拒绝《传送门》登陆Xbox因为游戏体积太大。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/portal-was-offered-to-xbla-but-rejected | title = Portal was offered to XBLA, but rejected | publisher = GamesIndustry.biz | date = 2008-04-28 | first = James | last = Lee | accessdate = 2008-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517110429/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/portal-was-offered-to-xbla-but-rejected | archive-date = 2008-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>《传送门：仍然活着》受到了评论者的好评，<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/portalstillalive | title = Portal: Still Alive (xbox360: 2008) | accessdate = 2008-10-27 | publisher = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081025071208/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/portalstillalive | archive-date = 2008-10-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的Andrew Hayward评论到，因为橙盒物美价廉还容易入手，《传送门》现在“比以往更强大”。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3170852&p=4 | title = Portal: Still Alive (Xbox 360) | date = 2008-10-27 | accessdate = 2008-10-27 | first = Andrew | last = Hayward | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120718021325/http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3170852&p=4 | archivedate = 2012-07-18 }}</ref>在[[IGN|IGN]]的排名前十的Xbox Live Arcade游戏中，《传送门：仍然活着》位居第五。编辑Cam Shea认为该游戏和橙盒捆绑销售，因此排名有一定的争议，不过他仍然对游戏的新地图表示赞扬。<ref>{{cite web |title=IGN's Top 10 Xbox Live Arcade Games |url=http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/980/980538p1.html |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2009-08-07 |date=2009-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413173841/http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/980/980538p1.html |archive-date=2012-04-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>后来的2010年9月，《传送门：仍然活着》的排名被改为第七。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://xboxlive.ign.com/articles/112/1120887p1.html | title = The Top 25 Xbox Live Arcade Games | publisher = IGN | date = 2010-09-16 | accessdate = 2010-09-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100918065519/http://xboxlive.ign.com/articles/112/1120887p1.html | archivedate = 2010-09-18 }}</ref>

=== 模组 ===
《传送门》已形成了一个[[游戏模组|模组]]社区，用户可设计自己的地图包或进行更深层次的修改。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=178414 | title = Portal Maps Investigated | publisher = CVG | date = 2008-01-05 | accessdate = 2008-01-05 | first = Ed | last = Zitron | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080107094419/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=178414 | archive-date = 2008-01-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.thinkingwithportals.com/|title= Thinking With Portals|publisher= ThinkingWithPortals.com|accessdate= 2008-06-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150830161148/http://www.thinkingwithportals.com/|archive-date= 2015-08-30|dead-url= yes}}</ref>此外也有一些基于《传送门》的衍生作品。例如：

*一个名为“We Create Stuff”的团队在[[橙盒|橙盒]]发布之后开发了基于[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]的传送门游戏，叫做《'''Portal: The Flash Version'''》。该Flash版本受到了社区的好评。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogs.pcworld.com/gameon/archives/005669.html | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5w4mZY7A8?url=http://blogs.pcworld.com/gameon/archives/005669.html | archivedate = 2011-01-28 | title = Portal: The Flash Version | publisher = [[PC_World|PC World]] | first = Matt | last = Peckham | date = 2007-10-11 | accessdate = 2008-05-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>后来团队将其转换成可在原版《传送门》中游戏的地图包。<ref>{{cite web | title = Flash Version of Portal Converted to Actual Map Pack | url = http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/52522 | first = Nick | last = Breckon | date = 2008-05-05 | accessdate = 2008-05-05 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5w4mDsLWX?url=http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/52522 | archive-date = 2011-01-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
